{
  "stem": "1033.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a spoon and a tin can.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, my tendency is to pick up clues that you say-- and take me other places than what your question implies.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I will try and stick to the question.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People that influenced me inside the camp-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the interpersonal relationships between the inmates, or the other Jews, or the other people there, were increasingly more and more isolated.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were practically no interpersonal relationships that I am aware of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were drawn into their own world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whatever energy or life or spark of life they had, they spent it on themselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's like a, a 'going inside oneself' experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People heard what we had to do-- lining up, going to get food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then you went into your own world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was hardly any conversation that I recall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just waiting, waiting, waiting, and, and observing one's own breath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and in my own case, I thought of God a lot, but not in a religious sense, but in a-- in a-- in a-- as a power source-- as a-- as a-- as a-- as some-- as some-- something, someone, some entity, of which I felt a part of.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and that-- I am sure that has played a role in the fact that I did survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In terms of how we lived, we slept on concrete floors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were wooden posts inside the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was a chimney in the middle of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a long building, maybe 100 feet long and maybe 50 feet wide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "These are-- I never thought about this-- just as I recall them and try and picture them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was a '3 feet by 3 feet' chimney running along horizontally on the floor that separated the barracks into two halves.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a small room as you entered, which I suppose belonged to the-- to the Blockalteste, which was the leader of the block.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was responsible for the numbers, and who-- we were piled in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were wooden-- square, wooden beams supporting the roof.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The roof was maybe 7 feet high-- a V-shaped roof.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as we got in there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somebody said, sleep, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then we just all scoot down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we fitted in like sardines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so my knees were in somebody else's knees.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, and we laid on the stone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And, and, and, and the day was finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The interesting thing was that when someone turned, everybody [LAUGHS] had to turn, because there was no way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And, and, and we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it got to be a reflex action.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But in terms of [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] mental activity or spiritual or physical activity-- beyond the fact that one tends to salivate and thank God the stomach contracts when it doesn't get food-- there was just this notion that one was breathing.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was another day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we had to line up for Appell again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Role models in the camp-- I was amazed about my mother's brother, Uncle Sandor-- my great-uncle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But he never-- I never-- he never brought me any food or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He and his brother were very close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But beyond any question, had he not forced another person into this place-- and thereby saving my life-- today, I would not have a family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I, I can-- on one hand, I feel dreadful to, to live, in a manner of speaking, two lives-- the person who died, and my own.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And it's, it's, it's a notion that a normal person can't understand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But it did happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It's, it's the truth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had very little contact with the guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At every Appell time, which was every day, we were standing there for hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A, a guard walked and marched by and counted us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were dismissed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, we-- in Birkenau, nobody worked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a transit camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now, in, in, in Kaufering, in Lager 1, before I-- after I got thrown out of the kitchen, but before I went to Landsberg, to Lager I-- I worked with a Kommando on the railroad.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were picking up stones from the railings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were lighthouses, switching stations-- I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were just carrying-- picking up stones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's what we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And some of them were friendly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And sometimes, they allowed us to build a little fire so we could warm our hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was-- it was one day after another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they read their newspapers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had no idea of what was going on in the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
